        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "Demonstrate the use of a lambda function with the `filter()` function by keeping only even numbers in a list and printing the result.\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
